<h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
<p>Updated 3/25/2020</p>

<h4>How do I add my swimmers?</h4>
<p>
  You must be an admin monitor to add or edit swimmer information. Visit the SWIMMERS page under your account. From there, you can click ADD SWIMMER to add swimmers one-at-a-time. Alternatively, you can click IMPORT SWIMMERS to upload a spreadsheet of swimmer information to create them in bulk.
</p>
<br>

